quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  21,11,Heewii ko Men halki immorde e saare laatinoonde ko too√Īunde Men fu…ó…ói …ďaawo mayre yim…ďe goo
  21,12,"Tuma nde …ďe so'unoo Lepte Amen …óen, tawi kam…ďe hi…ďe doga …óe"
  21,13,"Wata on dogu, ruttee faade e ko neemina…óon kon e mu'un e ko…óan…óe mo'on, belajo'o on lannditoyte"
  21,14,"∆Āe wi'a: \"Eeyoo, bone amen, pellet, menen men laatinoke too√Īu…ďe\". @Corrected"
  21,15,"Seerataa ndun noddaandu ma…ď…ďe, haa Men wa…óa …ďe co√Īateeri ko …ďe may…ďe"
  21,16,Men tagaali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji ko Men fijoo…ďe
  21,17,"Sinndo Men faandino nde Men jogotoo fijindaaru, Men jogitotono …óum immorde ka Amen si tawii Men laatike wa…óoo…ďe"
  21,18,"Ko woni, Me…óen werloo Goonga kan e dow meere nden ka munca nde, tawa kayre ko nde fuuyoore, no woodani on bone kon ko sifoto…óon"
  21,19,"Ko Kanko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi …ďen wonu…ďe ka Makko kadi …ďe mawnittaako gaayi rewugol Mo, …ďe hasrintaaka kadi"
  21,20,Hi…ďe Subhinoo jemma e √Īalorma …ďe aamataa
  21,21,"Kaa …ďe jogiti rewetee…ói ka leydi hara kannji hi…ói immintina [may…ďe …ďen]"
  21,22,"Sinndo laatino e majji [kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin] rewtee…ói ko wonaa Alla …ói bonayno. Senayee wonanii Alla Jom Arsi kin gaayi ko…ďe sifotoo. @Corrected"
  21,23,"O lanndetaake ko O gollata kon, kam…ďe ko …ďe lannditoytee…ďe"
  21,24,"Kaa …ďe jogiti gaanin Makko rewetee…ói? Maaki: \"Addee daliili mon on, ko ndee woni jaŇčta …ďen wonndu…ďe e am e jaŇčta …ďen adii…ďe lam\". Ko woni, …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe …ďe anndaa Goonga kan kam…ďe ko …ďe …óurnii…ďe"
